metadata.description:
Street art in the metaverse is an important part of city life.

Lots of young pepes love to spend their summer days outside with friends, painting boring gray walls and fences, adding more bright colors and fun to the world!

And then, walking along them in autumn, look at the bright pictures and remember the summer warmth and sun.
